data.description: Welcome to the gated community of Cobblestone! This spacious 3,126 sq ft home has four bedrooms, two and a half baths, two living areas, and an office. The generously sized kitchen with granite countertops, offers plenty of room for cooking, meal preparation, and gathering with family and friends. The open layout allows for easy movement and interaction within the kitchen, breakfast nook, and living room. The electric cooktop also has a gas hookup capability. The large formal dining room is the ideal setting for family meals, holiday feasts, and celebratory gatherings. The custom dining room table and seating is included with the home. The expansive game room upstairs is perfect for gatherings or leisure time. The primary bedroom is a sanctuary of comfort, complete with an ensuite that includes a large walk-in shower, a double vanity sink, and a roomy closet. This home boasts a spacious backyard that offers ample outdoor living and recreational space.  The JB Woolf custom shed is spacious enough to accommodate various needs, such as storage, hobbies, or a workshop. This home offers ample living space for all to enjoy. Minutes away from Loop 1604 and conveniently located near shopping, dining, schools, and entertainment. The amenities for this community include a swimming pool, basketball court, and play area. Motivated Seller! Don't miss the opportunity to make this gorgeous home your own.
